org.panthercode.arctic.core.processing.modules

Class Loop

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.panthercode.arctic.core.processing.modules.AbstractModule
      • org.panthercode.arctic.core.processing.modules.Loop
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Identifiable, Versionable, Module
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Counter, Repeater

    public abstract class Loop
extends AbstractModule
    Class to repeat module's functionality. The Loop class provides some basic functions to control the loop process.
